  "title": {
   "en": "Gishi no Kawari ni, Yomei Ichinen to Iwareru Koushaku Shisoku-sama to Konyaku suru Koto ni Narimashita"
  },
  "altTitles": [
   {
    "ja": "義姉の代わりに、余命一年と言われる侯爵子息様と婚約することになりました"
   }
  ],
  "description": {
   "en": "Edith is an orphaned girl who is treated coldly by her step-parents and stepsisters. One day, her stepsister is offered a marriage proposal to Lionel, the eldest son of the Count of Granvelle, a very prestigious family. However, there is a reason for this proposal... so Edith becomes engaged to him instead of her stepsister.\n\n\"I'm sorry, I can't believe you're engaged to me like this. Can you just bear with me for one year?\"\n\nHer fiancé has only one year to live, but pure love brings about a miracle in this happy love story!",
   "ja": "義父母と義姉に冷たい仕打ちを受けている天涯孤独の少女・エディス。ある時、義姉に超名門・グランヴェル伯爵家の長男・ライオネルとの縁談が舞い込んできた。しかしこの縁談は実は訳ありで…、急遽エディスが義姉の代わりに婚約することになった。「ごめんね、こんな僕と婚約だなんて。一年だけ我慢してもらえる？」。"
  },
